{"tid":1469231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[賽後檢討] 請準備螢光棒 必要時為衝動勇武手足/搞事內鬼扣上","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:27:29.000Z","uid":100567,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd7d3def992a2675c39f6aeb539e2586d03f763","tid":1469231,"uid":100567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:02:01.000Z","msg":"[賽後檢討] 前線手足請準備螢光棒，當情況快將失控時，為衝動勇武手足/疑似搞事內鬼，扣上背囊，咁樣日後文宣會易做好多，正如中央是如何幫示威者扣上港獨帽子一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Am42ASy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAm42ASy.jpg&h=2e467c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一定要冷靜，我都好嬲，但記住邊個冷靜，邊個先會贏。<br />\n<br />\n最後，核爆都唔割。完"},{"pid":"aba393f564e91029f48990d19b86dc2d0e2645be","tid":1469231,"uid":100567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:04:22.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"bd67f0691e6f9ac7c7c70d735d4148e1c239c137","tid":1469231,"uid":100567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:06:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b3aa38a9d16da2bf5b5ae6114440efef54512e20","tid":1469231,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55164394056fea2571eadc361f83530402d69a9e","tid":1469231,"uid":7832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:11:43.000Z","msg":"[捉鬼大師]鬼 從來係無需要捉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460872\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460872</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d1fdc49ec9c3a23ade29c4c08f3c4778a38d9119","tid":1469231,"uid":163324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:19:44.000Z","msg":"螢光棒呢D暗號話變就變啦 而家仲通哂天 買物資好過啦"},{"pid":"d88f22a8de050e792c52713f09616a1806c7c782","tid":1469231,"uid":100567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:27:29.000Z","msg":"popo已經唔會再用螢光棒<br />\n螢光棒只係做文宣比市民睇<br />\n因為所有市民都知道之前警察係用螢光棒記認<br />\n<br />\n純討論，有錯請指正"}]}